/**
 * CartDrawer.astro — slide-over cart + the site-wide cart runtime.
 * Included once per page by Layout.astro.
 *
 * CONTRACT (used by every component that touches the cart):
 *  - Storage: localStorage "ti-cart-v1" → { items: [{ id, slug, name, priceEur, image, color, size, qty }] }
 *    id = slug + "|" + color + "|" + size (empty strings when N/A).
 *  - Global API: window.TICart = { add(item), remove(id), setQty(id, qty), get(), count(), subtotal(), open(), close() }
 *  - Events on document: "ti:cart:changed" (after any mutation), "ti:cart:open".
 *  - Declarative buttons (no JS needed in components):
 *      [data-add-to-cart] with data-slug, data-name, data-price, data-image,
 *